35:01.920 --> 35:04.000
Elements, atoms, and so forth are fundamental.

35:04.000 --> 35:07.920
And that therefore neurons and brains are part of objective reality.

35:08.720 --> 35:11.840
And that somehow when you get matter that's complicated enough,

35:12.720 --> 35:17.760
it will somehow generate conscious experiences by its functional properties.

35:17.760 --> 35:23.040
Or if you're panpsychist, maybe in addition to the physical properties of particles, you add

35:24.000 --> 35:27.120
